description: San Antonio is experiencing the most exciting uprising since the Battle of The Alamo now that Revolutionary Wings is rolling through the city and shaking up the food truck scene. With 20+ years of executive experience in the restaurant & hospital industry, Chef Joshua Paprocki is changing the world of mobile food service with his radically tasty selection of gourmet wings, exclusively made with all-natural chicken and locally sourced ingredients. San Antonians are loving every morsel from this eclectic menu of chef-inspired creations, from the perfectly buttery and spicy traditional Buffalo wings to the delicious twist on Belgian Chicken & Waffles (with waffle-dipped wings glazed in maple butter and sprinkled with powdered sugar). For this and much more, come liberate your appetite at Revolutionary Wings.
name: Revolutionary Wings
